#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A special <quote>trump</quote> game is called the Grand. In this game no "
"suit is trump and only the four Jacks count as trump. This game type is "
"indicated by the symbol of a Jack's head [8] on the score board [6]."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If player starts the round he has a choice of cards to play with, either a "
"card from a suite or a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only the face up cards from the player's own stack can be used to play the "
"round."
msgstr ""
"Ke hraní v kole mohou být použity pouze karty z hráčova balíčku otočené "
"lícem nahoru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player who wins the round starts the next one."
msgstr "Hráč, který vyhraje kolo, začíná další."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player who wins the round adds values of the cards played in that round "
"to his/her score."
msgstr ""
"Hráči, který vyhraje kolo, se do skóre připočtou hodnoty karet odehraných za "
"toto kolo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player with more than 60 points wins the game."
msgstr "Hráč s více než 60 body vyhrává hru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "If both players finish with 60 points each the game ends in a draw."
msgstr "Skončí-li oba hráči s 60 body, hra končí remízou."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each game a certain amount of victory points is awarded and added to the "
"overall score."
msgstr ""
"Za každou hru se uděluje určitý počet bodů. Ty jsou připočteny do celkového "
"skóre."

