#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategie a tipy"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
"cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards that "
"are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of those "
"cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the same suit, "
"he can play with any other card including a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is at least one <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest "
"<quote>trump</quote> wins both cards."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is no <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest card of the suit "
"played by the starting player wins both cards."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no "
"<quote>trump</quote> card, he has to play any card and the starting player "
"wins both cards."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The player who wins the round leads the next one."
msgstr "Hráč, který vyhraje kolo, vede další."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Často kladené otázky"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I play with a different deck of cards?"
msgstr "Můžu hrát s jinou sadou karet?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Refer to <link linkend=\"deck_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Ano. Viz <link linkend=\"deck_change\">tato</link> část 'Náhledu na "
"rozhraní'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Udělal/a jsem chybu. Mohu tah vrátit?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Tato hra nepodporuje možnost <quote>Zpět</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Mohu při hraní použít klávesnici?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Tuto hru nelze hrát pomocí klávesnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Nevím jak hrát dál! Jsou zde rady?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Tato hra nepodporuje možnost <quote>Poradit</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Musím ukončit svoji hru ještě před dokončením. Můžu uložit svůj průběh?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Save State</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. Tato hra neumožňuje <quote>Uložit stav</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change players' names?"
msgstr "Můžu změnit jména hráčů?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the names displayed on the right hand side of the game screen "
"refer to <link linkend=\"name_change\">this</link> section of 'Interface "
"Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Ano. Chcete-li změnit jména hráčů zobrazená na pravé straně obrazovky, "
"přejděte do <link linkend=\"name_change\">této</link> části 'Náhledu na "
"rozhraní'."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Náhled na rozhraní"

